race.comment: AVERRED (3) strode forward early from his wide draw to settle just off the lead last start then lifted to score by one length at this track over 1500m. Sure to measure up again. DECARBONISE (5) showed good early speed from the inside draw last time and stalked the lead before fading to finish sixth over 1800m at Gold Coast. Will be handy in the run and should prove hard to run down. GOLD DAZZLER (1) was too good for a maiden field last start over 1400m at Gatton, scoring by a nose. Tougher task this time but expected to be competitive again. MAEVE (8) has hit the top-five in ten of her past 11 starts and is a must for the exotics players.
